Thank you for your feedback to our new app version! As always you help us to improve the translator. According to your wishes we ve prepared 2.0.2 update with the following improvements: Fixed problem with translation when tapping Go button on some devices. The button to copy the entire translation on iPhone is returned. Scrolling of input field and translation area on iPhone are improved. Fixed problems with form clearing and keyboard appearance on iPhone. The last active language pair remains unchanged on application restart. Message appears on how to install a phrasebook if it is still not installed. Minor bug fixes. Also version 2.0.0 is the biggest update in the last 2 years: New modern intuitive and responsive interface which is tailored to your iPad or iPhone with a lot of usability improvements New long expected languages right to the summer vacation period! We ve added translation from Arabic Turkish Greek Catalan and Kazakh to Russian and English and back. Font size adjustment. Context menu in the dictionary use long tap on every translation variant . Bug fixes. If you enjoy this update please rate us and leave your vote in App Store. It s the best way to inspire us for the new excellent improvements.

With the new version Online Translator.Com became even quicker and more conveniently because we made for you two absolutely new opportunities iOS 8 or later : Add a new widget of Online Translator.Com for instant translation of clipboard. Use the Action button to send a link or text from any app for translation in Online Translator.Com. To enable a widget open the Today screen in the Notifications Center in iOS 8 scroll it down and click Change. Then click near Online Translator.Com and the Ready button. All you have to do now is to copy a text to the clipboard open the Today screen and translation of the copied text appears on the screen. To enable Actions extension click Share in any app for example in Safari choose More from the list of actions and then add Online Translator.Com to the list. Pronunciation speed improvement
